title: Google drops global vaccine requirement to enter buildings, says 'world is in a very different place'
description: "The world is in a very different place," a Google global security vice president said in a companywide memo.

title: To improve your finances, learn your 'money script,' psychologist says
description: Most people's financial behavior can be explained by the "money script" they learned as children and are probably still following, psychologist says.

title: I tried the world's most expensive sandwich: A $214 grilled cheese covered in edible gold
description: Orders for Serendipity3's "Quintessential Grilled Cheese" normally need to be placed 48 hours in advance in order for ingredients to be flown in.

title: Lamborghini CEO says orders for hybrid Revuelto show 'incredible' demand from wealthy car-buyers
description: The high-performance automaker has already sold out Revuelto orders for the first two years of production, CEO Stephan Winkelmann told CNBC.

title: Banks in 'more precarious situation' creating risks for global growth, IMF chief economist warns
description: Banks may pull back on lending, clouding the growth outlook — but central banks should stay focused on inflation, Pierre-Olivier Gourinchas told CNBC.

title: Ford to invest $1.3 billion to build EV manufacturing hub in Canada
description: The plant will build the company's next-generation EVs that are expected to arrive to market around mid-decade.

title: IMF cuts GDP forecasts, says global economy heading for weakest growth since 1990
description: The IMF said that five years from now, global growth is expected to be around 3% — the lowest forecast in a World Economic Outlook for over 30 years.

title: 'Unfinished business': Biden visits Northern Ireland as political tensions persist
description: U.S. President Joe Biden arrives in Northern Ireland on Tuesday to mark the 25th anniversary of the Good Friday Agreement — a landmark peace deal that effectively ended decades of conflict.

title: China releases rules for generative AI like ChatGPT after Alibaba, Baidu launch services
description: The Cyberspace Administration of China's draft rules on generative AI come after tech giants Alibaba and Baidu launched their own ChatGPT-style products.

title: CNBC Daily Open: Bitcoin breaches $30,000 as the economy slows
description: Markets were mostly unchanged Monday, though bitcoin breached $30,000. Investors are waiting for bank earnings and price reports.

title: Japanese trading houses rise as Warren Buffett says he plans on buying more
description: Buffett said he was "very proud" of these investments and that he plans to meet with the companies to emphasize Berkshire Hathaway's support.

title: Bitcoin tops $30,000 for the first time since June ahead of key inflation data; ether nears $2,000
description: Bitcoin topped the key psychological level of $30,000 as investors awaited key inflation data later in the week that could steer crypto prices.

title: Alibaba to roll out its rival to ChatGPT across all its products
description: Alibaba Cloud, the cloud computing unit of Chinese tech giant, announced it will be rolling out its own ChatGPT-style product Tongyi Qianwen in "the near future."

title: CNBC Daily Open: State of the economy: Slowing, but strong
description: Markets were mostly unchanged Monday. Investors are waiting for bank earnings and price reports.
